accessibility.text: public class MethodIdentifier {     private final String name;     private final Class[] parameters;      public MethodIdentifier(Method m) {         name = m.getName();         parameters = m.getParameterTypes();     }       // we can save time by assuming that we only compare against     // other MethodIdentifier objects     public boolean equals(Object o) {         MethodIdentifier mid = (MethodIdentifier) o;         return name.equals(mid.name) &&                 Arrays.equals(parameters, mid.parameters);     }     public int hashCode() { return name.hashCode(); } }
